    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is currently not in reliable running order. It suffers from significant engine trouble, including a heavy knock and consistent overheating, and the transmission slips when shifting into higher gears. The body has noticeable rust on the rocker panels and several large dents, while the interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. This would be an ideal project for a mechanic or a source for spare parts, as it will require substantial mechanical and cosmetic restoration to be roadworthy again.",
