    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some minor fading on the hood, while the interior shows typical wear on the upholstery and carpet. Mechanically, it runs and drives well, though it may require routine maintenance like new tires or a brake service in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, functional car for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
