    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable and stylish ride? This car is in good condition and has been well-maintained, making it a great choice for your daily commute or weekend adventures! It runs smoothly and looks wonderful, showing just the expected minor wear from careful use. It's ready for a new owner who appreciates a solid, dependable vehicle that's been cared for.",
