      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? I\u2019m parting with this absolute gem and honestly, it\u2019s in incredible shape! It\u2019s been babied since day one\u2014sparkling clean, no scratches, and runs like a dream. You\u2019ve got to see it in person to believe how well-kept it is. I\u2019m so excited for the next owner to enjoy this beauty. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
