      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "This 2004 Honda S2000 AP2 represents a pinnacle of analog engineering, preserved in showroom condition. Under the hood, the longitudinal F22C1 2.2L DOHC VTEC engine remains in factory-spec, delivering a linear power band and an 8,000 RPM redline without a hint of oil consumption or valve-train noise. The 6-speed close-ratio manual transmission offers short-throw precision, channeling power through a Torsen limited-slip differential. Its structurally rigid X-bone frame is complemented by a pristine double-wishbone suspension and original staggered wheels. This unmodified example retains all factory VIN tags on every panel, showcasing a level of preservation rarely seen. For the enthusiast who demands mechanical perfection and a visceral connection to the road, this S2000 provides a benchmark driving experience with zero deferred maintenance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
