      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage, preserving its original, deep-gloss factory paint\u2014completely free of swirls, rock chips, or imperfections. Inside, the premium leather interior remains supple and fragrant, showing zero signs of bolster wear, while every electronic feature and switch functions with tactile precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, accompanied by a comprehensive binder containing every service record since new. With its flawless undercarriage and pristine engine bay, this is a rare opportunity to own a museum-quality example that satisfies the most detail-oriented enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
